{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 31141,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人討伐遠征……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Demon Subjugation Expedition..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31142,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい……結局、ランス様が来られずに中止に……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes... in the end, Lord Rance couldn't come, so it was cancelled...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31143,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　えっ、もしかしてあれからずっと……？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, could it be that ever since then... ?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31144,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ……探しているのですが、見つからず……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes... we've been searching, but haven't found him...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31145,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「その、すみません、ランス様が……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Um, sorry, but about Lord Rance...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31146,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いえ、シィルさんが謝られることではありません。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, this isn't something you need to apologize for, Seel-san.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31147,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　……それに、とにかく総統を見つけないと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Besides, we must find our Commander no matter what...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31148,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あー。アニキも相変わらずいないんだ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah. Big brother isn't around still, huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31149,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アルカネーゼさん……ええ、そうなんです。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Arcanese-san... yes, that's right.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31150,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どこに行かれたのか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I wonder where he has gone...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31151,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さっき、日立姫に泣きつかれたんだけど。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Just now, Princess Hitachi clung to me crying.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31152,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　東芝王子も、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Prince Toshiba too,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31153,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どこかに行ったっきりみたいなんだよなー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"seems to have gone somewhere and hasn't returned.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31154,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「東芝王子………………え、まさか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Prince Toshiba... eh, no way...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31155,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ここをこうして……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Like this here...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31156,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ゼンマイネジを重ねて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"stacking the wind-up screws...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31157,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「この辺りに武器が欲しいな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'd like a weapon around here.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31158,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　地底のモンスターをズバーッ！　とやれる奴」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Something that can slash through the underground monsters with a swoosh!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31159,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いいね、大型のソードを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Nice, let's try making a large sword\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31160,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　展開できるようにしてみようか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"that can be deployed.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31161,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「よしよし、かっこいい奴だぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, alright, it's a cool one.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31162,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「い、いましたっ……！　ランス様ーー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"H-He's here...! Lord Rance—!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31163,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん？　シィルにクリームちゃんに……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hm? Seel, Cream-chan...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31164,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんだ、どうかしたのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What's wrong? Did something happen?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31165,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どうかしたか、では！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Did something happen, huh!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31166,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ありません！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, nothing at all!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31167,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「作戦の日時は伝えましたよね！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I told you the date and time for the operation, right?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31168,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それをすっぽかすとは、どういう事ですか！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"How could you just blow it off like that?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31169,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちっちっ。分かってないな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tch, tch. You don't get it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31170,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　作戦より戦争全体に勝つことを考えるべきだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You should be thinking about winning the whole war rather than just the operation.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31171,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……っ……それとこれと、なんの関係が……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...What does that have to do with this and that...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31172,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クリームは目に見えて不機嫌になったが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Cream visibly became displeased,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31173,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それでも理性を働かせて理由を問う。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "yet she still kept her composure and asked for the reason."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31174,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちまちま雑魚魔人を潰しても意味はない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There's no meaning in taking out the small fry demons one by one.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31175,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　片付けるためには、ケイブリスを一点突破だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To clean them up, we have to break through at the single point: Cave Bliss.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31176,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人ケイブリス、を……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The demon Cave Bliss...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31177,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうだ。地中から行く」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Exactly. We'll go from underground.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31178,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「地中から……！　しかし、それは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"From underground...! But, that means...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31179,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「新しい坑道を掘り進む。従来の物は使わん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We'll dig new tunnels. We won't use the existing ones.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31180,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……なるほど、その手で……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I see... using that method...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31181,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そう上手く、いくのでしょうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Will that really go smoothly?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31182,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いかせるんだ。その為の準備をしてる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We will make it work. We're preparing for that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31183,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「わ、わ、すごい……私も手伝っていい？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A-Amazing... Can I help too?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31184,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もちろん。扱い方さえ分かれば、いけるはずさ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Of course. As long as you know how to handle it, you should be able to.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31185,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "マリアを含めた三人は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The three of them, including Maria,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31186,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ああでもないこうでもないと遠征準備の調整に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "became absorbed in adjusting the preparations for the expedition, trying this and that."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31187,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "没頭していった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They immersed themselves deeply."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31188,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスと東芝王子は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and Prince Toshiba,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31189,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ああでもないこうでもないと改造計画に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "were absorbed in their modification plans, trying this and that."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31190,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "没頭していった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They immersed themselves deeply."
    }
  ]
}

